Class RaceResultList

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc216.wolf_results.race_results.RaceResultList

  • public class RaceResultList
extends java.lang.Object
    RaceResultList class holds the list of results for one race - it can add a result and filter the results for the race

    Varsha Gopal, Abigail Ormond
